title: [Admission] Pes kcet counselling doubt
content:
I missed the jee pes counselling and have no clue about what to bring on the day of kcet oes counselling. They havent sent any mail or sms yet im assuming its the same documents as jee counselling?
Can someone help please

comments.body:
yes its same.  but now they postponed the kcet pes.   
instead its JEE PES round 2 will be held.    
so be ready for JEE PES Round 2

KCET counselling is delayed, now JEE counselling R2 will happen first  
And yeah you have to get the same things that was needed for R1 counselling

Wait so help me out are there seats reserved equally for both the kcet pes counselling and jee pes counselling like 40 percent is through general counselling is 30 percent saved for jee pes and 30 for jee cet counselling or are they just giving all seats available for jee counselling and remaining for cet because i saw the cutoffs even at 80 and below percentile aiml in ec campus was available which is insane to think of

not much exact info available on this. my guess is only 5% seates for KCET PES (as already 40% is available through KEA KCET).  
so 40-45% seats will be done through JEE  PES.  
No clear info but this is my guess based on round 1 counselling and the seats filled till now.  
note:  10-15% for mangement quota.
